des:
Ask Acclaim Federal Credit Union about products and services, rates, branch hours and
more from your Amazon Echo, Show, or Spot device. You can enable the skill by saying
“Alexa, enable the Acclaim skill” or by enabling it in the skills section of the Alexa app.

When you want information from Acclaim just say, “Open Acclaim”

General Information:
• “What is the routing number?”
• “Where are you located?”
• “What’s your phone number?”
• “Are you open?”

Membership Information:
• “How can I join?”
• “How do I open an account?”

Service Information:
• “What’s the rate for car loans?”
• What electronic services do
 you offer?
